es more than the deficits of the other candidates outweigh their strengths. Therefore, I support **Candidate\u202fB** for the long\u2011distance pilot position.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
