 criteria\u2014reliability, calmness under pressure, technical competence, and effective crew cooperation\u2014Candidate\u202fB offers the most balanced and safety\u2011critical profile. His core strengths outweigh the interpersonal shortcomings, which are less detrimental than the missing or negative attributes of the other candidates.\n**Vote:** Candidate\u202fB.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
